parameters:
Memimi: G-g-gosh... Bunny-chan... I can't take it anymore...
I'm going, I'm going to save her now...!

Anomalocaris: Wait... if we go out there now, it's bad
news!! If those thugs outside spot us, they'll tip off the
mayor to our hideout, and it's game over!!

Cerburus Octopus: Besides, how do you plan to rescue her
against that many? You'll just get caught too and dragged
into a gangbang party!! We need to endure this for now...

Memimi: But...! Bunny-chan... Bunny-chaaaan... To not be
able to go save her, this is just too cruel... waaah, Bunny-
chaaaan...

Shark Broccoli: Calm down, Shark Duke! Bunny-chan is a
formidable monster herself... Worrying unnecessarily is an
insult to her. The last thing she would want is for us to
get dragged down with her.

Brachiocondor: Right now, we need to focus on regaining our
strength! She'll eventually come back here... That's the
moment we strike!! We'll attack with all our might when
they're off guard after having their fun with Bunny-chan!

Memimi: ...ugh... o-okay... I need to calm down... hoo...
hoo... Bunny-chan... I'm sorry...

Anomalocaris: ...yeah, before that guy comes back, maybe I
should hit the bathroom... At this rate, there's a chance I
won't be able to fight properly...

Cerburus Octopus: Me too... kinda need to go... was keeping
an eye on the situation outside and... well, biological
urges...
Memimi: Maybe I should start by beating these guys up...

Dynamite Abalone: Wabibi~!! So you were hiding here, you
losers!! Bringing back two escaped bounties will surely
please Mayor Orca Broccoli!

Bunny-chan: Gyaaah, Dynamite Abalone!!? You've sided with
the mayor...?

Cerberus Octopus: Eeek... Eeeeek!! The strongest monster in
the city is now the mayor's underling...!? This is
impossible... it's all over...

Originally, Dynamite Abalone, the "Moist Powder Magazine,"
was supposed to be Memimi's final opponent in the Monster
Fight. Despite being knocked out in one hit by Mayor Orca,
no one doubts his strength as he now serves under him...

Dynamite Abalone: Wabiwabi... oh, Bunny-chan is here too!
I'm a boob man, I prefer you over flat-chested shark girls!!
Let me have a little taste...

Memimi: How rude, you bastard!! Who are you calling flat-
chested!!? Keep spouting nonsense and I won't forgive you,
you hear me!!

Dynamite Abalone: It's not nonsense if I've seen it
directly... they're small...

Memimi: Youuuuuu!!!! It seems I need to discipline you
before facing the mayor!! Come at me, trash... I'll knock
you out in one punch!!!

Anomalocaris Mosman: She's more furious than when the big
boss got taken down...
